    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Report: Module Overview -> Goal: Inform -> Method: Styled text block. | Report: Encounter List -> Goal: Navigate -> Method: Sticky nav with smooth-scroll JS. | Report: Fallacy Card Tables -> Goal: Organize/Drill-Down -> Method: Interactive JS/HTML accordion. This replaces the static table for a cleaner, interactive experience. | Report: Mana Costs ({1}{W}) -> Goal: Style -> Method: Custom CSS-styled inline spans to mimic MTG symbols without using images/SVG. Justification: This all-HTML/CSS/JS approach provides a dynamic, app-like feel for the game manual, making it a usable tool, not just a static document. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
